Of course she's also forgiving, idealistic and persuasive, but far less strongly and often mixed with being obsessive as well. Her elegance though, this is what she's so well-liked for. Friends usually count on this and her insight in times of need. All in all, Amanda has plenty of character faults too. Her irrational nature and venomous nature do cause plenty of friction and beyond what people are willing to deal with. Fortunately her brilliance usually softens the worst of it.

Unfortunately very few people like Ashley Collier, but the fact she's uncaring and scornful is only the begining. To make matters worse she's also extreme, disconcerting and perverse, but fortunately they're balanced out slightly by being insightful as well. But focus on her as this is what she's most disliked. Multiple nights have ended in disaster because of this and her callous nature, as sad of a reality as this may be. All in all, Ashley doesn't turn everything to dust. She's efficient and surprising among others, all considered it could be much worse. Unfortunately her uncaring nature is usually lurking and ready to spoil the fun.
